WEBVTT FILE:

00:00:00.850 --> 00:00:06.710
During the stateside duty, the problems you dealt with largely were the

00:00:06.710 --> 00:00:12.560
 boredom and the tedium of training and the like. And keeping your

00:00:12.560 --> 00:00:18.420
 team together and keeping morale up. In a combat or deployed situation

00:00:18.420 --> 00:00:24.280
 problems were just existing in doing your job which was vital in

00:00:24.280 --> 00:00:30.140
 compelling, and everything else kind of shrank beyond the necessity

00:00:30.140 --> 00:00:35.990
 of doing the best job you could because you knew everything you did

00:00:35.990 --> 00:00:41.850
 would make a difference as to whether someone lived or died

